sequenceDiagram
    participant USER as 👤 User
    participant NEMOCLAW as 🤖 NemoClaw Agent
    participant OPENSHELL as 🔒 OpenShell<br/>(L7 Proxy)
    participant GUARDRAILS as 🛡️ NeMo Guardrails NIM
    participant EMBED_NIM as 📐 Embedding NIM
    participant POSTGRES as 🗄️ PostgreSQL + pgvector
    participant RERANK_NIM as 🔢 Reranker NIM
    participant LLM_NIM as 🧠 Nemotron LLM NIM
    participant ANF_AGENT as 🧠 ANF Agent Memory

    USER->>NEMOCLAW: Send query via channel
    NEMOCLAW->>OPENSHELL: Route query through sandbox
    OPENSHELL->>GUARDRAILS: Input rail check<br/>(jailbreak, PII, topic)
    GUARDRAILS-->>OPENSHELL: Sanitized query
    OPENSHELL-->>NEMOCLAW: Cleared query
    NEMOCLAW->>ANF_AGENT: Load conversation history
    ANF_AGENT-->>NEMOCLAW: Recent context
    NEMOCLAW->>EMBED_NIM: Embed sanitized query
    EMBED_NIM-->>NEMOCLAW: Query vector
    NEMOCLAW->>POSTGRES: Hybrid search<br/>(HNSW vector + BM25 FTS + RRF merge)
    POSTGRES-->>NEMOCLAW: Top-N candidate chunks
    NEMOCLAW->>RERANK_NIM: Rerank candidates vs. query
    RERANK_NIM-->>NEMOCLAW: Reranked, top-K chunks
    NEMOCLAW->>OPENSHELL: Construct prompt<br/>(query + context + persona)
    OPENSHELL->>LLM_NIM: Forward prompt (credential injected)
    LLM_NIM-->>OPENSHELL: Generated response
    OPENSHELL->>GUARDRAILS: Output rail check<br/>(fact-check, PII, safety)
    GUARDRAILS-->>OPENSHELL: Validated response
    OPENSHELL-->>NEMOCLAW: Final response
    NEMOCLAW->>ANF_AGENT: Update memory (interaction log)
    NEMOCLAW-->>USER: Deliver grounded response
